How to build a debian package for lcg-info:

1. Create the following directory structure:

debian/
    |__ lcg-info/ 
               |__ DEBIAN/
                        |__ control
               |__ usr/ 
                     |__bin/
                          |__ lcg_info
                     | 
                     |__ share/
                             |
                             |__doc/ 
                                  |__ copyright
                                  |
                                  |__ changelog
                             |
                             |__ man/
                                   |
                                   |__ man1/
                                          |__ lcg-info.1

2. Run: dpkg-deb --build lcg-info
3. Rename lcg-info.deb to the right version lcg-info_x.y.z-r.deb


 
                                   
                            
